    <item>
      <title>2024 年失败后，华尔街对冲热潮再次兴起</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/wall-street-s-hedging-craze-gets-second-wind-after-2024-misfire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 2024 年欣欣向荣的市场中，最大的罪过就是怀疑。风险资产的白热化上涨让那些为了对冲和分散风险而购买华尔街大肆宣传的新产品的人的日子变得苦不堪言。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/wall-street-s-hedging-craze-gets-second-wind-after-2024-misfire</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 21:36:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>力拓和嘉能可就曾被视为禁忌的交易进行了数月谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/rio-and-glencore-spoke-for-months-about-deal-that-was-once-taboo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[十年前，嘉能可公司 (Glencore Plc) 提出与力拓集团 (Rio Tinto Group) 合并，但力拓在几天后就拒绝了。本周有消息称，去年下半年，两家公司花了几个月的时间进行谈判，这表明，就在大型交易热潮席卷全球采矿业之际，形势发生了变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/rio-and-glencore-spoke-for-months-about-deal-that-was-once-taboo</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 21:32:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
